#features.mb-5
  .container
    .row.justify-content-center
      .col-8.text-center
        %h2 A complete solution for your email signatures
        %p.lead.pb-5
          Signkit keeps getting stronger by the day, but here are some of our favorite features that help you manage email signatures with ease, today.
    .row
      - data.features.each do |feature|
        .col-6.pb-5
          .media.px-2
            = image_tag feature.icon, width: "40", class: "mr-3", style: "margin-top: -8px;"
            .media-body
              %h5.mt-0= feature.title
              = feature.description
